Type: Package
Package: gigs
Title: Assess Growth in Infants and Newborns
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-04-13
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Simon", family = "Parker", email = "simon.parker@lshtm.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given = "Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation", role = c("fnd", "cph"))
    )
Description: Convert between z-scores/percentiles and anthropometric measures in multiple growth standards, and classify
    infant growth accordingly. With a simple, single interface to the WHO Child Growth Standards and various
    INTERGROWTH-21st Standards, 'gigs' makes growth assessment easy and reproducible for clinicians, researchers and
    policy-makers.
